  "body": "As per the current optimistic spec consideration SAFE_SLOTS_TO_IMPORT_OPTIMISTICALLY must be user configurable with the cli param: `--safe-slots-to-import-optimistically`. Current it is set to a constant value `128` as recommended in the below mentioned PR.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/2770/files#diff-60fbcfca8d247fba1c2de905be0420919d57f519acfb02d27573235aa9d007ebR200-R202\r\n\r\nAdd this param in the cli for users to configure if required.",
